      "content": "i know... i've tried the talking part. i've tried the therapy and the friends. it's like talking about a hole doesn't stop you from being in it. it just feels like no matter what i do, the outcome is always the same. i'm just stuck in this pattern and i don't see how any of that changes the reality of it.",
